WEBVTT

00:00:02.914 --> 00:00:04.924
Shah Rukh Khan: The speaker who
you are going to hear now,

00:00:04.924 --> 00:00:07.163
has not walked the path
life was leading her on,

00:00:07.163 --> 00:00:10.019
but ensures that life always takes her
where she wants to go.

00:00:10.019 --> 00:00:11.678
Over the last 50 years,

00:00:12.329 --> 00:00:15.756
these decisions have made her
face opposition from society,

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.412
even distanced her from her loved ones,
put her in difficult situations,

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:23.341
but she faced each challenge fearlessly.

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:27.308
From the war zones of Afghanistan
to the threshold of her own home,

00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:29.805
she kept walking ahead
on the path chosen by her